nodes.text: Jedi strike team  (capture of the Sith Emperor)

During the Galactic War between the Galactic Republic and the reconstituted Sith Empire, the Jedi Master Tol Braga assembled a strike team of Jedi with the purpose of capturing and redeeming the Sith Emperor. Besides Master Braga, the team consisted of Jedi Knights Leeha Narezz, Warren Sedoru, Kira Carsen, and the Knight known only as the Hero of Tython. The team was also assisted by Sergeant Fideltin Rusk, Archiban Frodrick Kimble, also known as Doc, and the astromech droid T7-O1.
